Problem Statement
Creating a scientific calculator program with user menu driven operations
● Square root function - √x
● Factorial function - x!
● Natural logarithm (base е) - ln(x)
● Power function - xb


DevOps tool chain:


1. Using a source control management tool - like GitHub
2. Testing - test your code using either JUnite
3. Build - build code using  Maven
4. Continuous Integration - Continuous integrating code using Jenkins
5. Containerize - Containerize code using Docker.
6. Pushing created Docker image to Docker hub .
7. Deployment - Do configuration management and deployment using  Ansible. Using these do configuration management and pull your docker image and run it on the managed hosts.
8. Monitoring - for monitoring using the ELK stack. Using a log file to do the monitoring.
